episodes.title: Pam Bondi Explodes At Epstein Files Hearing | 10 News
episodes.description:
Survivors of Jeffrey Epstein's sex trafficking ring, on Wednesday, condemned the US Department of Justice's handling of the Epstein files after victims’ names were published and alleged abusers were redacted.

US Attorney General Pam Bondi attempted to defend her department’s handling of the files, but the exchange became heated, accusing congresspeople of engaging in “theatrics” when inviting her to apologise to victims present at the hearing.

Lawmakers have expressed frustration and anger at the amount of material in the Epstein files which has been redacted or withheld. Trump administration personnel has cited legal privileges as the reason for doing so.

episodes.title: King Charles Strips Prince Andrew Of Royal Titles, Londoners React To Royal Shake-Up | 10 News
episodes.description:
King Charles’ move to strip Prince Andrew of his titles and remove him from Royal Lodge has been confirmed by Buckingham Palace.

Andrew, now known as Andrew Mountbatten-Windsor, has been told to surrender his Windsor lease and relocate to private housing.

The decision has drawn mixed reaction on the streets of London, some say the decision was “long overdue”, given Andrew’s links to Jeffrey Epstein. However, others have expressed sympathy for the Duke’s wellbeing.

The Palace described the action as “necessary” and reiterated its support for abuse survivors.

Andrew maintains his innocence and continues to deny the allegations against him.
